  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a fighter, you gain the following class features.</p>\n<h5>Hit Points</h5>\n<p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d10 per fighter level</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 20 + your Constitution modifier</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d10 (or 6) + your Constitution modifier per fighter level after 1st</p>\n<h5>Proficiencies</h5>\n<p><strong>Armor:</strong> All armor</p>\n<p><strong>Weapons:</strong> Simple weapons, martial weapons</p>\n<p><strong>Tools:</strong> None</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Strength, Constitution</p>\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose two from Acrobatics, Animal Handling, Athletics, History, Insight, Intimidation, Perception, and Survival</p>\n<h5>Equipment</h5>\n<p>You start one of the following equipment options, in addition to the equipment granted by your background:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A chain shirt, a medium shield, a longsword, and a soldier's pack</li>\n<li>Leather armor, two daggers, a heavy crossbow with 20 bolts, 10 darts, and a soldier's pack</li>\n<li>A chain shirt, a greatsword, two javelins, and a soldier's pack</li>\n<li>Ring mail, a medium shield, a morningstar, a soldier's pack, and 5 gp</li>\n<li>100 gp worth of equipment and an equipment pack</li>\n</ul>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
